Is the joint account holder aware you are making a complaint against this PPI policy?


Yes
No








If you are complaining on behalf of both policy holders we will be unable to cancel a live PPI policy without joint consent.
If we decide to uphold your claim, any additional premiums paid from the date of our offer will not be refunded as part of this complaint.








 







