					Full Description



		Santander UK plc is a financial services provider, which offers a range of personal financial products and services. The Company's segments include Retail Banking, Commercial Banking, Global Corporate Banking and Corporate Centre. The Retail Banking segment offers a range of products and financial services to individuals and small businesses (with less than two directors, owners or partners), through a network of branches and automated teller machines (ATMs), as well as through telephony, digital, mobile and intermediary channels. The Commercial Banking segment offers a range of products and financial services to customers through a network of regional Corporate Business Centers (CBCs) and through telephony and digital channels. The Global Corporate Banking segment serves corporate clients and financial institutions that require specially-tailored services or value-added wholesale products. The Corporate Centre segment consists of the non-core corporate and treasury legacy portfolios.
